data.value: Eco path "The Vita Stena" starts from the village of Yavorets, located on the road between Sevlievo and Gabrovo in Stara Planina. The transition is about 22 km. On the way you can see the rock wreath "Vita Wall", whose caves have been found ancient vessels and objects of bone. It is possible to hire horses. There is a fountain and a relaxation area with benches and a table.
